  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/f5c2d51f48653cc9f8061d7f39d2d1cb.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>Bulletrooms is an old-school first-person shooter set in the Backrooms universe. You need to go through several levels of Backrooms, your only goal here is to survive and find a way out. Remember, all levels in Backrooms are inhabited by dangerous entities, but you don't have to run and hide anymore. Now, you can fight back!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/d469b361a6133afd444c4b381714d46b.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>In the mazes of Backrooms you can find an assault rifle, shotgun, laser, grenade launcher and rocket launcher. Use this entire arsenal to clear the Backrooms of dangerous entities!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e0215e6df012618de4e9f250d8f0283.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>Explore corridors and rooms that shouldn't exist in reality. The levels available to you are: The Lobby, Habitable Zone, Pipes, Sublimity, The Windows, The End, Level ! (RUN). Unique dangers and aggressive entities await you in each level!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/be026a23741d2eb73638f671e1642f0e.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>It is up to you to choose the entities that will populate the Backrooms. These can be canonical \"entities\" or nextbots They look different, but you can shoot them anyway!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/712f098ee1f08541123deb4e13861b91.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span>",
